WEBVTT

00:00.070 --> 00:01.273
<i>Previously on "Castle"...</i>

00:01.341 --> 00:03.652
They killed my mother.
What do you want me to do here?

00:03.719 --> 00:06.709
Beckett, everyone associated
with this case is dead.

00:06.788 --> 00:08.431
Walk away.
Well, last time I checked,

00:08.503 --> 00:11.651
it was my life, not your
personal jungle gym.

00:11.719 --> 00:13.560
I know you crawled inside
your mother's murder

00:13.629 --> 00:14.602
and didn't come out.

00:14.671 --> 00:16.357
The same way you hide in
these nowhere relationships

00:16.420 --> 00:17.802
with men you don't love.

00:17.885 --> 00:19.499
You know what we are, Castle?
We are over.

00:19.567 --> 00:21.228
Captain Montgomery's
part of the conspiracy.

00:21.287 --> 00:22.483
He's been lying to
us the whole time.

00:22.558 --> 00:23.724
Did you kill my mother?

00:23.797 --> 00:26.298
No, but she died because
of what we did that night.

00:26.367 --> 00:28.514
Then who killed her? No, Kate.
I give you a name. I know you.

00:28.618 --> 00:29.630
You'll run straight at him.

00:29.709 --> 00:31.028
I might as well shoot
you where you stand.

00:31.084 --> 00:32.020
Now they're coming.

00:32.085 --> 00:34.759
Castle, get her outta here.

00:35.280 --> 00:37.285
No! Please!

00:38.370 --> 00:40.579
Where is she, Roy?
You can't have her.

00:41.247 --> 00:42.742
You can't hide her from us.

00:45.245 --> 00:46.902
So that was what,
your last stand?

00:46.986 --> 00:48.443
I'm just gonna kill her anyway.

00:48.503 --> 00:49.782
No, you're not.

00:49.855 --> 00:51.076
And he's not.

00:51.145 --> 00:53.955
I saw to that.
You're done, Lockwood.

00:54.028 --> 00:56.528
We both are.

00:56.596 --> 00:59.665
No one outside of
this immediate family

00:59.750 --> 01:02.224
ever needs to know about this.

01:02.308 --> 01:03.657
As far as the world is concerned,

01:03.721 --> 01:05.586
Roy Montgomery died a hero.

01:07.019 --> 01:08.068
Kate!

01:08.139 --> 01:10.037
Oh! Oh, no!

01:10.142 --> 01:12.631
Kate. Stay with me, Kate.
Find the shooter!

01:13.005 --> 01:14.146
I love you.

01:14.353 --> 01:15.693
I love you, Kate.

01:20.448 --> 01:21.772
She's tachying out.

01:22.714 --> 01:23.594
Come on!

01:24.351 --> 01:26.280
Pulse ox... respiration...
Set up for intubation.

01:26.338 --> 01:27.715
78 over 56.

01:31.596 --> 01:34.017
Come on, Kate.
Don't you die on me.

01:34.088 --> 01:36.035
Stay with me. Stay with me.

01:36.095 --> 01:38.685
Single GSW to left chest.
Do not die.

01:38.750 --> 01:40.842
Come on, girl. Come on.
Set up for a chest tube. Trauma one.

01:40.902 --> 01:42.299
Switch. We got this.
This is my friend.

01:42.368 --> 01:43.938
You understand me?
She's my friend.

01:43.996 --> 01:46.040
Then let us save her life.

